TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SKU.FABRIC_CONT_CD as FABRIC_CONT_CD, SKU.STYLE_CD as STYLE_CD, SKU.ATTRIBUTE_CD as ATTRIBUTE_CD, SKU.COLOR_CD as COLOR_CD, SKU.SIZE_CD as SIZE_CD FROM SKU WHERE SKU.STYLE_CD IN (SELECT STYLE_CD FROM DA.STYLE WHERE ORIGIN_TYPE_CD='S')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_TLSTYL AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_TLSSFX AND COLOR_CD = I_TLCOLR AND SIZE_CD = I_TLSZCD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT X.GARMENT_FIBERCONTENT as GARMENT_FIBERCONTENT, X.SELLING_STYLE as SELLING_STYLE, X.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE as SELLING_ATTRIBUTE, X.SELLING_COLOR as SELLING_COLOR, X.SELLING_SIZE as SELLING_SIZE FROM LOGISTICS.SELLING_GARMENT_EXPLOSION X,DA.STYLE B WHERE X.SELLING_STYLE=B.STYLE_CD AND B.ORIGIN_TYPE_CD='S' AND GARMENT_FIBERCONTENT IS NOT NULL AND ROWNUM=1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELLING_STYLE = I_TLSTYL AND SELLING_ATTRIBUTE = I_TLSSFX AND SELLING_COLOR = I_TLCOLR AND SELLING_SIZE = I_TLSZCD
